          "provided"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " America with a decent idea of which areas of our country will be most devastated by climate change, and which areas will be most insulated from the worst effects. Unfortunately, it seems that population flows are going in the wrong direction — today’s new Census data shows a nation moving out of the safer areas and into some of the most dangerous places of all."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
