        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Similarly, the city of Philadelphia is comparatively well situated in the climate crisis — but it saw only modest population growth of 5 percent. It was surpassed on the list of biggest cities by Phoenix, which saw an "
